  "Description": {
    "English": "A beautiful blue crystal, this organic compound possesses both great hardiness and a shimmering translucence. It is harvested from the leaves of <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Frostwort</span>.<br><br>Frostwort requires <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen conditions</span> to thrive in the wild, but can be farmed in all environments with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hydroponics Tray</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种美丽的蓝色水晶，这种有机化合物极具耐寒性，并闪烁着半透明的微光。它可以从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">霜草</span>的叶子中收获。<br><br>霜草需要在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻条件</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种美丽的蓝色水晶，这种有机化合物极具耐寒性，并闪烁着半透明的微光。它可以从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">霜草</span>的叶子中收获。<br><br>霜草需要在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻条件</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種漂亮的藍色結晶有機化合物，不僅硬度極佳，還呈閃爍發亮的半透明狀。可從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">霜草</span>葉片上採收而得。<br><br>霜草需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰凍氣候</span>才能在野外生長，但若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">水耕盤</span>，便能在任何環境中栽種。"
  },
